data.name: Ninjitsu Art of Mosquito Marching
data.desc: Special Summon up to 2 Level 4 or lower Insect monsters with the same Level from your hand. If you control "Number 2: Ninja Shadow Mosquito": You can banish this card from your GY, then target face-up monsters your opponent controls, up to the number of Insect monsters you control; place 1 Hallucination Counter on each of them. (The effects of monsters with a Hallucination Counter are negated.) You can only use each effect of "Ninjitsu Art of Mosquito Marching" once per turn.
